How DOM Connects with JavaScript Engine
Now we enter real backend-level understanding.
JavaScript engine (like V8 in Chrome) does NOT directly know HTML.

It interacts with:
Browser APIs
The DOM is a Web API provided by the browser, not part of JavaScript itself.
